{"tid":1801272,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"快D黎學下德文簽名喇!!!!!","createTime":"2019-12-28T13:23:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T14:52:09.000Z","uid":20222,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bb5fbebb88e69eb00ecc145c429bf8cf56d36872","tid":1801272,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T13:23:16.000Z","msg":"Step 1. 打開Chrome 既broswer<br />\n冇既話去download<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/intl/zh-TW/chrome/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fintl%2Fzh-TW%2Fchrome%2F&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=e721713e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/intl/zh-TW/chrome/</a><br />\n<br />\nStep 2. 輸入以下網址<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_10%2F_01%2FPetition_99914.nc.html&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=4227e207\" target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html</a><br />\n<br />\nStep 3. 按下你滑鼠既右制, 然後選擇翻譯成英文(可以之後揀返轉做繁體中文)<br />\n<br />\nStep 4. 按下簽署請願書/Sign the petition <br />\n<br />\nStep 5. 你係需要註冊先至可以簽到名既<br />\n但係你識睇中文/英文應該難你唔到?<br />\n主要係打返曬EMAIL, PW, <br />\n假名/pseudonym 你求其打個名落去,有可能會撞左既, 撞左就轉名轉到OK 為止<br />\n個人資料打名, 姓, 街道號(我打HONG KONG)<br />\n郵遞區號 00000<br />\n位置打HONG KONG<br />\n國家揀HK<br />\n禁註冊<br />\n<br />\nStep 6. 去EMAIL 禁返條LINK<br />\n<br />\nStep 7. 再次輸入以下網址<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_10%2F_01%2FPetition_99914.nc.html&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=4227e207\" target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html</a><br />\n<br />\nStep 8. 再次按下簽署請願書/Sign the petition <br />\n<br />\nStep 9. 打EMAIL/PW之後禁下面信封果個制<br />\n<br />\nStep 10. 恭喜你睇曬成個教程, 亦都證明你係一個真正既和理非<br />\n<br />\n大家麻煩真係曬5分鐘時間去簽<br />\n我唔理你用假EMAIL簽到夠定係搵曬親戚朋友<br />\n快D同我簽爆佢!!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d956504ec30febd130b4e20955925241e2905858","tid":1801272,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T13:23:45.000Z","msg":"自推十次 1/10"},{"pid":"5b668e47b441d441d1cf3114d0fcf1ceaaae9361","tid":1801272,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T13:24:35.000Z","msg":"自推十次 2/10"},{"pid":"5e630c6525ca8c11b5cdc6186b27ff3944d300cc","tid":1801272,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T13:25:23.000Z","msg":"自推十次 3/10"},{"pid":"66035104daf083da64ec89a0fe9d697e4bc5dc9f","tid":1801272,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T13:25:39.000Z","msg":"自推十次 4/10"},{"pid":"5638289f729f98fa58306379451cb0a1f2243c75","tid":1801272,"uid":288648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T13:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e882e7b8a4cf5f6e210620d0a448159c48bbc6a","tid":1801272,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T13:26:07.000Z","msg":"自推十次 5/10"},{"pid":"1401754a5810c54360d991ad5189e7b7de1edcc1","tid":1801272,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T13:26:29.000Z","msg":"自推十次 6/10"},{"pid":"d9e65e822d2a232a8b015ee5f939f457e169cb55","tid":1801272,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T13:27:39.000Z","msg":"自推十次 7/10"},{"pid":"e87a31f5